 var LoadingStep = 0;

 var UHT_SEND_ERRORS = true;
 var UHT_HAD_ERRORS = false;
 
 window.onerror = function(messageOrEvent, source, lineno, colno)
 {
 
  if (!UHT_SEND_ERRORS)
	return;

  UHT_HAD_ERRORS = true;
	
  var args = null;

  if (messageOrEvent instanceof Event)
   args = [messageOrEvent["message"], messageOrEvent["fileName"], messageOrEvent["lineNumber"], messageOrEvent["columnNumber"]];
  else
   args = [messageOrEvent, source, lineno, colno];

  args[1] = String(args[1]).split("?").shift().split("/").pop();

  var msg = args[0] + " at " + args[1] + ":" + args[2] + ":" + args[3];
  ga('BehaviourTracker.send', 'event', "uht_errors", msg, URLGameSymbol, 1);

  window.onerror = null;
 };

 window.onbeforeunload = function()
 {
	var step = LoadingStep.toString() + (LoadingStep+1).toString();
	var lastStep = LoadingStep.toString();

	if (LoadingStep == 4)
	{
		step = "PLAYING";
		lastStep = "PLAYING"
	}

	ga('LoadingTracker.send', 'event', "uht_loading", "_CLOSED_error_" + step, URLGameSymbol, UHT_HAD_ERRORS?1:0);
 
	if (LoadingStep > 1)
		globalTracking.StopTimerAndSend("uht_loading", "_CLOSED_at_" + lastStep, "LoadingTracker");
 	else
		if (GA_timer_load_start != undefined)
			ga('LoadingTracker.send', 'timer', "uht_loading", "_CLOSED_at_1", URLGameSymbol, new Date().getTime() - GA_timer_load_start);

	UHT_SEND_ERRORS = false;

	if (SendTrackingIfQueued != undefined)
	{
		SendTrackingIfQueued();
		SendTrackingIfQueued();
		SendTrackingIfQueued();
		SendTrackingIfQueued();
	}
	
	return;
 }
 
 
 var game_symbol_from_url = (function()
 {
  var params = [];
  var urlSplitted = location.href.split("?");
  if (urlSplitted.length > 1)
  {
   var paramsSplitted = urlSplitted[1].split("&");
   for(var i = 0; i < paramsSplitted.length; ++i)
   {
    var paramSplitted = paramsSplitted[i].split("=");
    params[paramSplitted[0]] = (paramSplitted.length > 1) ? paramSplitted[1] : null;
   }
  }
  return params["symbol"];
 })();

 var game_symbol_from_url_value = game_symbol_from_url;

 if (game_symbol_from_url_value != undefined)
  URLGameSymbol = game_symbol_from_url_value;

var gaMapping = {};
function ga4_init( ua_id, ua_params, ga4_id)
{
	ga('create', ua_id, ua_params);
	var sampleRate = ua_params.sampleRate;
	if (ua_params.name != "WasabiTracker")
		sampleRate /= 10;
	if (Math.random() <= (sampleRate/100))
	{
		gtag('config', ga4_id, {
			send_page_view: false
		});
		gaMapping[ua_params.name] = ga4_id;
	}
}

<style>
    #logoContainer
    {
      margin: auto;
    }
    #logoInContainer,#logoOutContainer
    {
      position:absolute;
      z-index: 6969;
    }
    #loadingBarGradient
    {
      background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #f48d00, #fce85c, #f48d00, #ffae3b);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradient 20s ease infinite;
      height: 100%;
      bottom: 0px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: auto;
    }
    #gradientContainer
    {
      margin: auto;
      height: 100vh;
      position: fixed;
      bottom:0px; 
      width: 100%; 
      height: 2vh;
      z-index: 6969;
    }
    @keyframes gradient {
      0% {
        background-position: 0% 50%;
      }
      50% {
        background-position: 100% 50%;
      }
      100% {
        background-position: 0% 50%;
      }
    }
    #logoPPimg, #poweredByImg
    {
      margin: auto;
      height: 15vh;
      max-height: 200px;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    #logoPP
    {
      bottom: 10%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      height: 10vh;
      z-index: 6971;
    }
    #poweredBy
    {
      bottom: 10%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      height: 10vh;
      z-index: 6971;
    }
    #logoPPimg
    {
        -webkit-animation: fadeInFromNone 2s ease-out, flyIn 0.5s ease-out;
        -moz-animation: fadeInFromNone 2s ease-out, flyIn 0.5s ease-out;
        -o-animation: fadeInFromNone 2s ease-out, flyIn 0.5s ease-out;
        animation: fadeInFromNone 2s ease-out, flyIn 0.5s ease-out;
        animation-delay: 0.6s;

<script>
      var animationFinished = false;
      var shouldHide = false;
      var hideAlreadyCalled = false;

      window.HideLoaderFP = function()
      {
        if (!animationFinished)
        {
            shouldHide = true;
            return;
        }

        if (hideAlreadyCalled)
          return;

        hideAlreadyCalled = true;

        window.removeEventListener("resize", onResize, false);
        document.getElementById("logoHide").beginElementAt("0.5");
        document.getElementById("loadingBarGradient").style.animation="fadeInFromNone 0.5s reverse forwards 0.3s ease-out";
        document.getElementById("logoPP").style.animation="fadeInFromNone 0.5s reverse forwards 0.3s ease-out";
        document.getElementById("poweredBy").style.animation="fadeInFromNone 0.5s reverse forwards 0.3s ease-out";
        document.getElementById("gradientBallContainer").style.animation="fadeInFromNone 0.5s reverse forwards 0.3s ease-out";
        maskScaleAnimation.addEventListener("endEvent", () => {
            var logoContainer = document.getElementById("logoContainer");
            if (logoContainer != null)
              logoContainer.remove();
            var ppLogoAnim = document.getElementById("ppLogoAnim");
            if (ppLogoAnim != null)
              ppLogoAnim.remove();
            var loadingBarGradient = document.getElementById("loadingBarGradient");
            if (loadingBarGradient != null)
              loadingBarGradient.remove();
            var gradientBallContainer = document.getElementById("gradientBallContainer");
            if (gradientBallContainer != null)
              gradientBallContainer.remove();
          });
      }
      var onResize = function()
      {
        if (document.getElementById("gradientBall") == null)
            return;

        var height = window.innerHeight/1.33;
        var width = (1000 * height) / 720;
        var left = (window.innerWidth - width)/2;
        document.getElementById("gradientBall").style.width = width + "px";
        document.getElementById("gradientBall").style.height = height + "px";
        document.getElementById("gradientBall").style.left = left + "px";
      }
      window.addEventListener("resize", onResize, false);
      window.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", onResize, false);
      var registerAnimationEnd = function()
      {
        document.getElementById("logoPPimg").addEventListener("animationend", () => {
          animationFinished = true;
          if (shouldHide)
            HideLoaderFP();
        });
      }
      window.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", registerAnimationEnd, false);
</script>
